  "handbookContacts": "<p>Jefferson High School is one of five comprehensive high schools in the <strong>Jefferson Union High School District (JUHSD)</strong>, serving communities across northern San Mateo County.</p><h3>School Links</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net\" target=\"_blank\">Jefferson High School Website</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net/our-school/administration\" target=\"_blank\">JHS Administration Team</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net/our-school/staff-directory\" target=\"_blank\">JHS Staff Directory</a></li></ul><h3>District Links</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.juhsd.net/about-us/administration\" target=\"_blank\">JUHSD District Administration</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.juhsd.net/about-us/board-of-trustees\" target=\"_blank\">JUHSD Governing Board</a></li></ul><h3>Contact Jefferson High School</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Department</th><th>Phone</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Main Office</td><td><a href=\"tel:+16505507700\">(650) 550-7700</a></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"h-cta\"><div class=\"h-cta-title\">📞 Need to Reach Us?</div><div class=\"h-cta-body\">The Main Office is open Monday–Friday during school hours. For staff email addresses, visit the online staff directory.</div><div class=\"h-cta-actions\"><a href=\"tel:+16505507700\" class=\"h-cta-btn\">📞 (650) 550-7700</a><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net/our-school/staff-directory\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"h-cta-btn outline\">🔗 Staff Directory</a></div></div>",
